I"~U<p style="font-size: 24px"><strong>Rfam ID: <a href="https://rfam.xfam.org/family/RF00167,target=&quot;_blank&quot;">RF00167</a></strong> (Purine riboswitch)<br /></p>
<p style="font-size: 24px"><strong>    <a href="https://rfam.xfam.org/family/RF03165,target=&quot;_blank&quot;">RF03165</a>(2dG-II)</strong> <br /></p>

